    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入《仓鼠城市》，在这里，每一条道路和建筑都为您的食物采集帝国提供动力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195320/extras/d88afb658f92e7f5bd04bd789c610c01.poster.avif?t=1738788261\" width=450 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195320/extras/d88afb658f92e7f5bd04bd789c610c01.webm?t=1738788261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195320/extras/d88afb658f92e7f5bd04bd789c610c01.mp4?t=1738788261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造基础设施，解锁独特建筑，看着您的仓鼠繁荣发展，同时登上排行榜，成为终极首领！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在试玩版中，探索一座现代城市地图，其中包含<strong>9座独特建筑</strong>，每座建筑都具有独特的效果！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽快<strong>储存足够的食物</strong>，让你的仓鼠前往火星！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195320/extras/7649ade84587f71f3db616e71cd7e0f1.poster.avif?t=1738788261\" width=450 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195320/extras/7649ade84587f71f3db616e71cd7e0f1.webm?t=1738788261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195320/extras/7649ade84587f71f3db616e71cd7e0f1.mp4?t=1738788261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>建造与扩展：</strong> 修建道路和建筑，创建一座能最大化食物采集效率的城市。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>升级与竞争：</strong> 升级建筑，提升优势，与全球玩家在排行榜上一较高下。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>策略性城市规划：</strong> 每条道路、每座建筑、每次升级都能为资源采集带来助力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>可解锁的结构：</strong> 发现全新建筑，为您的仓鼠帝国增添更多策略深度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>放置模式：</strong> 《仓鼠城市》会在您离开时自动运行，随时回来都能看到欣欣向荣的城市！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195320/extras/c72e13cc1eb87b3e4b04338c2cacec37.poster.avif?t=1738788261\" width=274 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195320/extras/c72e13cc1eb87b3e4b04338c2cacec37.webm?t=1738788261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195320/extras/c72e13cc1eb87b3e4b04338c2cacec37.mp4?t=1738788261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快来加入我们的 <strong>Discord 社区</strong>，成为游戏的测试玩家吧！</p>",
